To enable collaborative tagging, connect to Supabase (free):

  1. Go to supabase.com and create a free account
  2. Create a new project (any name, e.g., "photo-tagger")
  3. Go to SQL Editor and run this query:
create table tags (
  id uuid default gen_random_uuid() primary key,
  x float not null,
  y float not null,
  name text default '',
  created_at timestamp default now()
);

alter table tags enable row level security;
create policy "Allow all" on tags for all using (true) with check (true);
